I'm now revisiting promise handling in `App.tsx` and focusing on the correct data retrieval from `FileList`. I'm now making the code clearer by using `async/await` to resolve file content. Meanwhile, in `StatisticsDisplay.tsx`, I'll explicitly assert `data` as `PlaybackStat` inside the spread operation to avoid type inference issues. I've updated the relevant files and XML.


